 demoDrawBoxes(form posn size rows cols);sf;boxsize;starts;n;colours;sizes;radii
⍝ Draw a subform and put boxes in it

 sf←form,'.BX'
⍝ sf ∆WC'SubForm' ('Posn' posn)('Size' size)
 boxsize←size÷rows cols
 n←≢starts←⌊,(¯.95++⍳rows cols)×⊂boxsize
 sizes←n⍴⊂⌊0.9×boxsize
 radii←5 5 ⍝ n⍴⊂5 5
 colours←n⍴⊂0 0 0 ⍝ Black
 (sf,'.R1') ∆WC'Rect' (↓⍉↑starts) (↓⍉↑sizes) (radii) colours
